{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"WakeLock.request()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WakeLock/request","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Screen_Wake_Lock_API\">Screen Wake Lock API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WakeLock\"><code>WakeLock</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><em><code>request()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Screen Wake Lock API 的相关页面</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/wakeLock\"><code>Navigator.wakelock</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WakeLockSentinel\"><code>WakeLockSentinel</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>这是一个实验中的功能</strong><br>此功能某些浏览器尚在开发中，请参考<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">浏览器兼容性表格</a>以得到在不同浏览器中适合使用的前缀。由于该功能对应的标准文档可能被重新修订，所以在未来版本的浏览器中该功能的语法和行为可能随之改变。</p></div><div class=\"notecard secure\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>安全上下文:</strong> 此项功能仅在<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Security/Secure_Contexts\">安全上下文</a>(HTTPS), 一些 <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">支持的浏览器</a>.</p></div>\n<p><strong><code>WakeLock.request()</code></strong> 方法用来获取屏幕唤醒锁定权限，防止屏幕变暗、关闭或展示屏幕保护程序。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">WakeLock.request(wakeLockType)\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"wakelocktype\"><code>wakeLockType</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>唤醒锁定类型，目前必须传 <code>\"screen\"</code> 。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<p>决议为 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WakeLockSentinel\"><code>WakeLockSentinel</code></a> 的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"异常","title":"异常","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"notallowederror\"><code>NotAllowedError</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>当唤醒锁定不可用的时候抛出，例如在：</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>由于屏幕唤醒锁定策略，Document 不允许使用屏幕唤醒锁定。</li>\n      <li>Document 不完全激活。</li>\n      <li>Document 被隐藏。</li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/User_agent\">User Agent</a> 无法获取平台的唤醒锁定。</li>\n    </ul>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下示例获取屏幕唤醒锁定并在 10 分钟后释放它：</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">function tryKeepScreenAlive(minutes) {\n  navigator.wakeLock.request(\"screen\").then(lock =&gt; {\n    setTimeout(() =&gt; lock.release(), minutes * 60 * 1000);\n  });\n}\n\ntryKeepScreenAlive(10);\n</pre>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/screen-wake-lock/#the-request-method","title":"Screen Wake Lock API"}],"query":"api.WakeLock.request"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.WakeLock.request","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WakeLock/request/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关链接","title":"相关链接","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WakeLock\"><code>WakeLock</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/wakeLock\"><code>Navigator.wakeLock</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"相关链接","id":"相关链接"}],"summary":"WakeLock.request() 方法用来获取屏幕唤醒锁定权限，防止屏幕变暗、关闭或展示屏幕保护程序。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WakeLock.request()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"WakeLock.request()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/wakelock/request","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/wakelock/request/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WakeLock","title":"WakeLock"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WakeLock/request","title":"WakeLock.request()"}],"pageTitle":"WakeLock.request() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}